int GET_NTH_CLOSEST_VEHICLE_NODE_ID(float x, float y, float z, int nthClosest, int nodeFlags, float zMeasureMult, float zTolerance);Parameters:x: X coordinatey: Y coordinatez: Z coordinatenthClosest: The index of the node to returnnodeFlags: Node flags, see GET_CLOSEST_VEHICLE_NODEzMeasureMult: How strongly the difference in the Z direction should be weightedzTolerance: How far apart the Z coords have to be before zMeasureMult kicks inReturns: Returns the nth closest vehicle nodes id.
